PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 68 - which (a) declares that the forest fires in July 2003 which affected the Town of Norman Wells, in the NORTHWEST TERRITORIES, to be of concern to the federal government; and (b) authorizes the provision of financial assistance in that regard.
